					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hey! I'm happy to say that the magnificent <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theshipening" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2926243&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579640066" alt="Theshipening" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2926243)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theshipening" >Theshipening</a></span> and I have translated this hub, and quite a lot of its works in French, <a href="http://fondationscp.wikidot.com/those-twisted-pines-hub">just here</a>. Those Twisted Pines is one of my favorite pieces of work on the wiki, as well as Anderson Robotics. We intend to translate the whole story of Vince, Merlo and her family, and more! Working on your tales and SCPs is always a pleasure.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
