				<wikidot:authorName>stormbreath</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3075960</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>With Conwell's approval, I've added my <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3310">SCP-3310</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rainier-night">Rainier Night</a> to this canon. Both are set in the Pacific North West (in Crater Lake National Park and Rainier National Park, respectively).</p> <p>As a note: a tale I wrote about SCP-3310 (<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/on-the-outskirts">On the Outskirts</a>) is also set within the PNW, but is set within the Broken Masquerade. As such, I didn't add it to this hub, but it's sorta Twisted Pines-adjacent.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
