					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6229507#post-3848318</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6229507/those-twisted-pines-hub#post-3848318</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 Jun 2018 07:46:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>GreenWolf</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1814684</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Trust Conwell to create the single largest canon on the site overnight. He never does anything by halves.</p> <p>In all seriousness, it's great to finally have a central hub for all of these stories, and I'm proud of my contributions to this canon. Twisted Pines has been an ongoing influence on most of my writing, and collaborating with you has always been fun. There's a lot of overlap between this and Third Law as a result, but I've always thought of Twisted Pines as part of the extracanonical continuity &#8212; it's nice to see that sentiment is shared here. Both canons are only improved by their association with each other.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6229507#post-3848251</guid>
				<title>Strange things are done in the Northwest Rains...</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6229507/those-twisted-pines-hub#post-3848251</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 Jun 2018 06:21:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Summertime is the best time for breaking out those new canon hubs.</p> <p>This canon is the culmination of about six years worth of work, both from myself and several contributors that helped bring the world, characters, and stories of &quot;Those Twisted Pines&quot; to life. I look forward to seeing what new additions are made in the coming years.</p> <p>Thanks to my collaborators in creating this hub:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529826162" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" >Zhange</a></span> - Artwork - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/zhange-artwork">Zhange's Artwork Page</a></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529826162" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span> - The Crossroads blurb - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/hotline-eventide">Hotline: Eventide</a></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529826162" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" >GreenWolf</a></span> - UIU blurb - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/unusual-investigations">The Unusual Investigations of Kenneth Spencer and Robin Thorne</a></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" ><img class="